# Project Structure

## Playbook execution order
Play 0: `proxmox_backup` (back up host config + VMs)
Play 1: `proxmox_bridges`, `proxmox_pci_passthrough`, `openwrt_vm` (provision)
Play 2: `openwrt_configure` (configure OpenWrt via raw SSH)
Play 3: Bootstrap cleanup (remove temp IP)

## Key files
- `setup.sh` -- bootstrap venv + deps
- `run.sh` -- source .env + run playbook
- `cleanup.sh` -- restore/full-restore/clean subcommands
- `test.env` -- test machine config (committed)
- `.env` -- production secrets (gitignored)

## Test machine
- IP: configured via `PROXMOX_HOST` env var (test default: `192.168.86.201`)
- Node name in Proxmox: `home`
- Inventory host: `home` (in `inventory/hosts.yml`)
- Host vars: `inventory/host_vars/home.yml`

## Image management
- OpenWrt `.img` stored in `images/` directory (gitignored)
- `openwrt_image_path` defaults to `images/openwrt.img` (relative to project root)
- Absolute paths are also supported
